    "description": "Become an archer in a land called Arlan. Complete various tasks to unlock new locations to explore. Play with others in an open multiplayer room or play by yourself in single player mode. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147170/extras/0ba6a0f16acad126e3a9f955e71c02f9.avif?t=1767122040\" width=512 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2>This is an open world game and you are free to explore the different areas you unlock at your own pace. Keep an eye on your stamina as you travel, and pack food in your inventory for when you need it. Use your map to discover ruins, towns, and giant trees along the way. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147170/extras/51ae1eaeb4a497d26744ad06a43e426e.avif?t=1767122040\" width=512 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hunt</h2> Hunt elk and bear with your bow and collect steak from them. Ignite sticks to cook the steak, making the steak edible.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147170/extras/dc9fa8f245ccc73c77502edeed861c3c.avif?t=1767122040\" width=512 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sail</h2>Journey the sea with a ship, and discover places to fish for sailfish and seabass. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147170/extras/de4ad2c35fa3d857870cc778b8c34715.avif?t=1767122040\" width=512 height=64 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2>Customize your avatar and play with others in a public room. Includes multiplayer features such as space bubbles, blocking, reporting, friending, groups, communities, and more.",
